title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Element
description:
The ride it all addiction of today’s all-mountain snowboarder is nicely fed with the Element, which was designed to deliver rootsy style and high-end performance in the trees, steeps, powder, park, groomers, and well beyond; the quintessential do everything design.
To learn more about the Element visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/element/
